This folder includes a Matlab implementation of the central segmentation approach 
only for research use. 
The method is described in:

H. Wang and J. Oliensis, Shape Matching by Segmentation Averaging, ECCV08.



Before using the code, you need type 

mex diffSDis.c

in Matlab in this folder. 
There is a demo file showing how it works.


Each file has a brief description. 
For detail explanation, please check our paper.

Hongzhi Wang
01 July 2008
